array into a Set for O(1) lookup
compareSecurityOverviewWithBaseline() classifies each finding as:
introduced — fingerprint not in baseline
persistent — fingerprint present in baseline
resolved — fingerprint in baseline but not in current findings
summarizeBySeverity() counts findings per severity bucket per category

